column8: Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers, becoming less likely this afternoon. Winds southeasterly 20 to 30 km/h tending easterly 15 to 20 km/h in the evening then becoming light in the late evening.

Cloudy. Medium (40%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and early evening. Light winds becoming east to southeasterly 15 to 20 km/h in the morning then becoming light in the middle of the day.
Partly cloudy. Light winds becoming southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the afternoon then becoming light during the evening.
Mostly sunny morning. Slight (30%) chance of a shower, most likely in the afternoon and evening. Light winds.
Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm. Light winds becoming south to southwesterly 20 to 25 km/h during the day.
Partly cloudy. Slight (20%) chance of a shower. Winds southwesterly 15 to 20 km/h tending southerly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
